<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="dark" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Política de Privacidad | GastroFlow</title>
<meta name="description" content="Política de Privacidad y Tratamiento de Datos Personales de GastroFlow.">
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="/js/tailwind-landing.js"></script>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
  .glass { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; }
  .prose-legal h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface, #e2e8f0); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose-legal h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface, #e2e8f0); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prose-legal p  { margin-bottom: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .prose-legal ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
  .prose-legal ul li { margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
  .prose-legal a  { color: #818cf8; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background text-on-background">

<!-- Header -->
<header class="sticky top-0 z-[100] w-full bg-surface/80 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-md border-b border-outline-variant h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-12">
  <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2" style="text-decoration:none;">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">local_fire_department</span>
    <span class="font-bold text-xl text-primary tracking-tight">GastroFlow</span>
  </a>
  <a href="/auth/login" class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Iniciar Sesión</a>
</header>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 pt-16 pb-6">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">shield</span>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface">Política de Privacidad</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
    Última actualización: <strong class="text-on-surface">30 de junio de 2026</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
    Vigente desde: <strong class="text-on-surface">30 de junio de 2026</strong>
  </p>
  <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-xl glass text-sm text-on-surface-variant border border-yellow-500/20 bg-yellow-500/5">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined align-middle text-yellow-400 mr-1" style="font-size:1.1rem;">info</span>
    Este documento es una plantilla de uso interno. Se recomienda revisarla con un abogado especializado antes de publicarla oficialmente.
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contenido -->
<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 pb-20 prose-legal text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
  <%- settings.privacy_policy %>
</main>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="border-t border-outline-variant py-8 px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
    <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Inicio</a>
    <span class="hidden md:inline">·</span>
    <a href="/legal/terminos" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Términos y Condiciones</a>
    <span class="hidden md:inline">·</span>
    <a href="/legal/privacidad" class="text-primary font-medium">Política de Privacidad</a>
    <span class="hidden md:inline">·</span>
    <a href="mailto:privacidad@gastroflow.app" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">privacidad@gastroflow.app</a>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-on-surface-variant">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> GastroFlow Technologies. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
